i-role-5g-network/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2019%2F04%2F30%2Fuks-foreign-minister-urges-caution-huawei-role-5g-network%2F&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmR%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=691e45a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/04/30/uks-foreign-minister-urges-caution-huawei-role-5g-network/</a><br />\n<br />\n老婆係中國西安人嘅外交大臣主動呼籲提防華為...<br />\n此地無銀嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa55b926311602cb1df63a60fcf020a190461b9","tid":1134333,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d91c6453b9497845c9e88bdae48c46208898f52","tid":1134333,"uid":37111,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"e2a7ccd4529e809521a82543f79789180691f761","tid":1134333,"uid":237425,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T17:56:41.000Z","msg":"英國果個外交大臣?個老婆都好似係支那西<br />\n一陣又係間諜就笑撚到仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T18:28:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/04/30/uks-foreign-minister-urges-caution-huawei-role-5g-network/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2019%2F04%2F30%2Fuks-foreign-minister-urges-caution-huawei-role-5g-network%2F&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmR%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=691e45a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/04/30/uks-foreign-minister-urges-caution-huawei-role-5g-network/</a><br />\n<br />\n老婆係中國西安人嘅外交大臣主動呼籲提防華為...<br />\n此地無銀嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T18:30:13.000Z","msg":"咁就是睇下佢老婆係咪紅底啦<br />\n最起碼係大陸仲有無兩老? 有無資產"},{"pid":"1a7c3f8eaf32a5b81f80a2ef9e310b1010a8e9f1","tid":1134333,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T19:11:51.000Z","msg":"我等睇Trump 回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"232f202f0d43eb222772f485dff1754de4845adb","tid":1134333,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T20:45:28.000Z","msg":"&bull; The Prime Minister's decision follows a high-profile probe into revelations released from a top secret meeting<br />\n&bull;The leak of her controversial decision over contracts for the 5G phone network sparked a full-scale inquiry<br />\n&bull;The information came from a meeting of the National Security Council including intelligence chiefs last week <br />\n&bull;The spotlight was on the five ministers who were said to have voiced objections to the Huawei decision <br />\n&bull;Mr Williamson said he 'strenuously' denied involvement in the leak and said he refused to resign<br />\n&bull;Labour Tom Watson said: 'If he has leaked from the NSC Gavin Williamson should be prosecuted'<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/05/01/18/12965994-6981725-Mr_Williamson_told_the_BBC_that_he_was_not_the_source_of_the_lea-a-5_1556731645109.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F05%2F01%2F18%2F12965994-6981725-Mr_Williamson_told_the_BBC_that_he_was_not_the_source_of_the_lea-a-5_1556731645109.jpg&h=d824f97b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Mr Williamson told the BBC that he was not the source of the leak and that neither he nor his team would do such a thing.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/05/01/19/12970022-0-image-a-16_1556736476596.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F05%2F01%2F19%2F12970022-0-image-a-16_1556736476596.jpg&h=eedb5d9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Williamson was nicknamed Private Pike after the youthful innocent Dad's Army character played by Ian Lavender (pictured above on a stamp issues last year to mark the sit-com's 50th anniversary)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/05/01/18/12966212-6981725-image-a-6_1556731645110.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F05%2F01%2F18%2F12966212-6981725-image-a-6_1556731645110.jpg&h=3093f96e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/05/01/19/12968554-6981725-image-a-11_1556734323691.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F05%2F01%2F19%2F12968554-6981725-image-a-11_1556734323691.jpg&h=36324d8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Mr Williamson later sent his own letter continuing to protest his innocence and revealing he refused to resign, saying it would have implied guilt<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/05/01/21/12973844-6981725-image-m-31_1556742992905.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F05%2F01%2F21%2F12973844-6981725-image-m-31_1556742992905.jpg&h=602a82a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Penny Mordaunt leaves the Ministry of Defence (left) after being appointed UK Secretary of State for Defence<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/05/01/21/12973856-6981725-image-m-34_1556743010432.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F05%2F01%2F21%2F12973856-6981725-image-m-34_1556743010432.jpg&h=03884c45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n She spoke to journalists soon after being given the position (right)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/05/01/21/12973680-6981725-image-a-17_1556742669612.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F05%2F01%2F21%2F12973680-6981725-image-a-17_1556742669612.jpg&h=58ccb7dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Mr Williamson has been replaced by International Development Secretary Penny Mordaunt (pictured outside the Ministry of Defence today) - a Royal Navy reservist - who becomes the first ever female Defence Secretary<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/05/01/21/12967340-6981725-Gavin_Williamson_pictured_has_been_sacked_over_the_leaks-a-19_1556742881450.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F05%2F01%2F21%2F12967340-6981725-Gavin_Williamson_pictured_has_been_sacked_over_the_leaks-a-19_1556742881450.jpg&h=a5339f20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Gavin Williamson (pictured) has been sacked over the leaks<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/05/01/21/12967760-6981725-image-a-22_1556742924009.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F05%2F01%2F21%2F12967760-6981725-image-a-22_1556742924009.jpg&h=f884bf51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/05/01/21/12967774-6981725-image-a-24_1556742927328.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F05%2F01%2F21%2F12967774-6981725-image-a-24_1556742927328.jpg&h=ad79da23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2019/05/01/5268754679242469980/1024x576_MP4_5268754679242469980.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideos.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2019%2F05%2F01%2F5268754679242469980%2F1024x576_MP4_5268754679242469980.mp4&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmR%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=7bdac161\" target=\"_blank\">https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2019/05/01/5268754679242469980/1024x576_MP4_5268754679242469980.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2019/05/01/1002233294749188193/1024x576_MP4_1002233294749188193.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideos.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2019%2F05%2F01%2F1002233294749188193%2F1024x576_MP4_1002233294749188193.mp4&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmR%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=378e73d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2019/05/01/1002233294749188193/1024x576_MP4_1002